音频HAL 直接替换hardware/rockchip/audio/tinyalsa_hal代码


开启btsnoop_hci方法
setprop persist.bluetooth.btsnooppath /data/misc/bluetooth/logs/btsnoop_hci.log
setprop persist.bluetooth.btsnoopenable true
setprop persist.bluetooth.btsnooplogmode full

adb pull /data/misc/bluetooth/logs/btsnoop_hci.log
adb pull /data/misc/bluetooth/logs/btsnoop_hci.log.last

打电话时蓝牙可能不停断开重启，这个是固件原因,AP6398S我提供的是这个固件，如果你们有其它模块请找正基拿新固件
adb push BCM4359C0_003.001.006.0174.0433.hcd /vendor/etc/firmware//BCM4359C0.hcd



